title: Judge threatens to sanction SEC over ‘misleading’ statements in crypto case
description:
U.S. District Judge Robert Shelby issued a stern warning to Securities and Exchange Commission (SEC) attorneys regarding possible sanctions for “misleading” court proceedings in a lawsuit against the cryptocurrency firm Debt Box, according to court filings. The SEC secured a temporary restraining order against Debt Box via statements that were later proven to be false. […]
